1
00:01:21,400 --> 00:01:21,920
This...

2
00:01:28,720 --> 00:01:29,240
She...

3
00:01:29,640 --> 00:01:30,960
What's wrong with her?

4
00:01:31,520 --> 00:01:32,039
How should I know?

5
00:01:32,039 --> 00:01:32,970
I'm not a doctor.

6
00:01:34,360 --> 00:01:35,160
Doctor...

7
00:01:36,240 --> 00:01:36,840
You know medicine.

8
00:01:36,840 --> 00:01:37,840
Take a look at her.

9
00:02:23,840 --> 00:02:25,920
Why did the silver needle change color?

10
00:02:25,920 --> 00:02:26,280
She...

11
00:02:26,280 --> 00:02:27,480
She's been poisoned.

12
00:02:29,280 --> 00:02:31,920
And this poison is very peculiar.

13
00:02:32,520 --> 00:02:33,320
It seems

14
00:02:33,760 --> 00:02:36,280
to be the same poison found in the victim

15
00:02:36,440 --> 00:02:37,700
at the Prince's Manor.

16
00:02:38,800 --> 00:02:41,200
Did they follow us here?

17
00:02:41,200 --> 00:02:43,600
But why poison this girl?

18
00:02:46,320 --> 00:02:47,250
There's no time.

19
00:02:47,320 --> 00:02:49,640
This poison is extremely potent.

20
00:02:49,840 --> 00:02:51,560
Although this area is full of exotic plants

21
00:02:51,560 --> 00:02:53,000
and various herbs,

22
00:02:53,000 --> 00:02:55,120
I don't have time to process them.

23
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:57,400
I'll take her down the mountain

24
00:02:57,400 --> 00:02:58,320
to find a clinic

25
00:02:58,640 --> 00:03:00,770
and get her some ready-made medicine.

26
00:03:09,600 --> 00:03:11,560
What is this?

27
00:03:13,720 --> 00:03:16,800
I was bored last night, so I whittled this thing.

28
00:03:17,320 --> 00:03:19,320
It saves me from having to carry you.

29
00:03:25,880 --> 00:03:27,040
Thanks.

30
00:03:34,920 --> 00:03:36,240
You're so nervous.

31
00:03:36,360 --> 00:03:38,920
You rushed to see the owner as soon as you woke up.

32
00:03:38,920 --> 00:03:40,850
Could it be that you know this girl?

33
00:03:41,760 --> 00:03:43,880
That girl fainted as soon as she walked in.

34
00:03:43,880 --> 00:03:44,880
It's a trick.

35
00:03:48,680 --> 00:03:50,140
I actually don't know her.

36
00:03:50,720 --> 00:03:51,579
It's just that,

37
00:03:52,600 --> 00:03:53,720
as a healer,

38
00:03:54,000 --> 00:03:55,720
this is what I should do.

39
00:03:56,600 --> 00:03:57,720
What if it were a villain?

40
00:03:57,720 --> 00:03:58,980
Would you save him too?

41
00:03:59,000 --> 00:04:01,160
The law decides good and evil.

42
00:04:01,360 --> 00:04:03,220
I can't just leave someone to die.

43
00:04:04,880 --> 00:04:05,880
Let's go.

44
00:04:25,720 --> 00:04:26,600
By the way,

45
00:04:27,120 --> 00:04:28,760
I only poisoned you.

46
00:04:28,760 --> 00:04:30,820
How did you know I practice medicine?

47
00:04:31,160 --> 00:04:32,920
Medicine and poison have always been linked.

48
00:04:32,920 --> 00:04:33,920
You use poison so well,

49
00:04:33,920 --> 00:04:36,120
so your medical skills must be good too.

50
00:04:38,200 --> 00:04:40,680
I just didn't expect the Prime Minister's Manor to be so open-minded.

51
00:04:40,680 --> 00:04:43,120
Allowing the Prime Minister's daughter to mix with all sorts of people.

52
00:04:43,120 --> 00:04:45,850
If it were me, my father would have broken my legs.

53
00:04:47,080 --> 00:04:48,440
You're quite smart.

54
00:04:49,480 --> 00:04:52,400
If most people knew I was a woman,

55
00:04:52,400 --> 00:04:53,159
they would think

56
00:04:53,159 --> 00:04:55,440
I have no right to practice medicine.

57
00:04:56,520 --> 00:04:59,520
My teachers have called me a prodigy since I was young.

58
00:04:59,600 --> 00:05:02,120
Seeing through someone is easy for me.

59
00:05:02,560 --> 00:05:03,400
A prodigy?

60
00:05:05,120 --> 00:05:07,040
A prodigy who can't even ride a horse?

61
00:05:07,040 --> 00:05:08,440
That's because my father

62
00:05:10,320 --> 00:05:12,080
wouldn't let me go out.

63
00:05:12,160 --> 00:05:13,720
I've never even seen a horse.

64
00:05:13,720 --> 00:05:16,240
Otherwise, how could a mere foal stop me?

65
00:05:25,360 --> 00:05:27,920
I am naturally relieved this is not the Heir,

66
00:05:28,160 --> 00:05:29,560
but I am still uneasy.

67
00:05:30,440 --> 00:05:32,000
You may not know, Doctor Ji,

68
00:05:32,280 --> 00:05:33,880
the Heir rarely leaves home.

69
00:05:34,120 --> 00:05:35,880
The outside world is dangerous,

70
00:05:35,880 --> 00:05:37,280
and I fear he cannot cope.

71
00:05:42,960 --> 00:05:44,400
His figure...

72
00:05:45,640 --> 00:05:46,280
What?

73
00:05:47,159 --> 00:05:49,800
Captivated by my dashing good looks?

74
00:05:50,200 --> 00:05:51,720
Father once said,

75
00:05:51,960 --> 00:05:54,960
the Heir of Prince Zhenbei was strictly disciplined.

76
00:05:54,960 --> 00:05:56,520
He is an upright gentleman.

77
00:05:56,520 --> 00:05:58,920
How could he be so frivolous?

78
00:05:59,760 --> 00:06:01,440
Perhaps I am overthinking.

79
00:06:04,240 --> 00:06:05,720
You are shy.

80
00:06:06,120 --> 00:06:07,040
Walk slower.

81
00:06:07,040 --> 00:06:08,570
I'm carrying someone here.

82
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:10,920
I said walk slower,

83
00:06:10,920 --> 00:06:12,120
not stop suddenly.

84
00:06:12,680 --> 00:06:14,200
Someone fainted.

85
00:06:20,840 --> 00:06:23,360
Young people sleep so well these days.

86
00:06:23,840 --> 00:06:25,240
They can sleep anywhere.

87
00:06:29,000 --> 00:06:30,120
He's poisoned.

88
00:06:31,440 --> 00:06:32,700
Another poisoned one.

89
00:06:33,760 --> 00:06:35,960
Is this mountain poisonous?

90
00:06:40,159 --> 00:06:41,960
Did he eat poisonous mushrooms?

91
00:06:43,960 --> 00:06:44,760
Probably.

92
00:06:53,640 --> 00:06:54,200
Help...

93
00:06:54,200 --> 00:06:55,120
Help me...

94
00:06:56,480 --> 00:06:57,080
Here.

95
00:06:57,720 --> 00:06:59,040
Get up.

96
00:07:02,320 --> 00:07:04,880
Thank you for saving my life, Miss.

97
00:07:05,280 --> 00:07:06,280
I induced vomiting just now,

98
00:07:06,280 --> 00:07:08,240
to expel the poisonous mushrooms.

99
00:07:08,240 --> 00:07:10,640
But you still need to drink plenty of water.

100
00:07:10,920 --> 00:07:11,520
Here.

101
00:07:12,480 --> 00:07:13,480
Drink some water.

102
00:07:16,480 --> 00:07:18,480
You must go down to a clinic soon.

103
00:07:18,480 --> 00:07:19,600
Don't delay treatment.

104
00:07:19,600 --> 00:07:20,600
To tell the truth,

105
00:07:20,920 --> 00:07:22,880
I am from the clinic in Sitai Town,

106
00:07:22,880 --> 00:07:24,410
the eldest son of Master Du.

107
00:07:25,240 --> 00:07:27,520
I was hungry just now,

108
00:07:28,040 --> 00:07:30,120
so I found some mushrooms.

109
00:07:30,240 --> 00:07:32,320
I misjudged them and fainted here.

110
00:07:32,320 --> 00:07:34,120
Thank you both for saving me.

111
00:07:35,200 --> 00:07:36,000
Ah.

112
00:07:36,159 --> 00:07:37,920
Isn't this Miss Chuyun?

113
00:07:38,159 --> 00:07:39,480
Where did you find her?

114
00:07:42,040 --> 00:07:42,900
Do you know her?

115
00:07:43,159 --> 00:07:44,240
Of course.

116
00:07:44,440 --> 00:07:46,100
She is Squire Chu's daughter.

117
00:07:46,720 --> 00:07:49,120
They are a wealthy family in Sitai Town.

118
00:07:49,440 --> 00:07:51,570
A tragedy befell her family recently.

119
00:07:52,240 --> 00:07:53,570
They were all wiped out.

120
00:07:53,640 --> 00:07:55,520
The killer was never found.

121
00:07:55,920 --> 00:07:57,650
Miss Chuyun went missing, too.

122
00:07:57,800 --> 00:08:00,040
The authorities have been looking for her for a long time.

123
00:08:00,040 --> 00:08:02,170
We found her in a cabin on the mountain.

124
00:08:02,200 --> 00:08:03,880
Miss Chuyun just fainted.

125
00:08:03,880 --> 00:08:06,280
She needs medical attention immediately.

126
00:08:07,720 --> 00:08:08,680
In that case,

127
00:08:08,760 --> 00:08:10,080
let's go down the mountain together.

128
00:08:10,080 --> 00:08:11,810
We can go to my family's clinic.

129
00:08:13,160 --> 00:08:14,290
That would be great.

130
00:08:14,520 --> 00:08:15,650
Please lead the way.

131
00:08:16,040 --> 00:08:17,120
Okay.

132
00:08:18,920 --> 00:08:20,040
Let's go.

133
00:08:23,520 --> 00:08:25,000
He's suspicious.

134
00:08:25,520 --> 00:08:28,240
Even I know not to eat wild mushrooms.

135
00:08:28,240 --> 00:08:29,640
He's from a medical hall,

136
00:08:30,200 --> 00:08:31,480
yet he's so absurd.

137
00:08:32,240 --> 00:08:32,720
True.

138
00:08:32,720 --> 00:08:35,360
But this girl's illness can't wait.

139
00:08:35,799 --> 00:08:38,120
Let's see what he's up to.

140
00:08:39,559 --> 00:08:41,880
Don't worry, I'm here.

141
00:08:42,360 --> 00:08:44,760
Whatever he's up to, it won't work.

142
00:08:46,400 --> 00:08:47,760
Childish.

143
00:08:49,400 --> 00:08:50,200
You...

144
00:09:00,520 --> 00:09:01,450
You have issues.

145
00:09:01,960 --> 00:09:02,760
Sir,

146
00:09:02,960 --> 00:09:04,760
you've carried Miss Chuyun for a long time.

147
00:09:04,760 --> 00:09:06,000
You must be tired.

148
00:09:06,360 --> 00:09:07,960
I've mostly recovered.

149
00:09:08,240 --> 00:09:09,720
Let me help you.

150
00:09:19,120 --> 00:09:21,120
Sitai Town is just down the mountain.

151
00:09:21,120 --> 00:09:22,120
The path is rugged,

152
00:09:22,120 --> 00:09:23,120
so stay close.

153
00:09:25,960 --> 00:09:28,020
He's pretty good at carrying people.

154
00:09:32,480 --> 00:09:33,880
You're not bad yourself.

155
00:09:37,920 --> 00:09:39,720
You walk like an old lady.

156
00:09:40,440 --> 00:09:41,770
Want me to carry you too?

157
00:09:44,720 --> 00:09:46,280
That won't be necessary.

158
00:09:59,400 --> 00:10:02,660
It's not a good thing for a clinic to have booming business.

159
00:10:03,120 --> 00:10:04,320
Things are a bit unusual today.

160
00:10:04,320 --> 00:10:06,040
Please wait here for a moment.

161
00:10:06,560 --> 00:10:08,120
I'll take her in through the back door.

162
00:10:08,120 --> 00:10:09,250
Why not go together?

163
00:10:09,520 --> 00:10:12,560
Miss Ji Bai is skilled in medicine and can help with the treatment.

164
00:10:12,560 --> 00:10:14,160
My father is a bit eccentric.

165
00:10:14,520 --> 00:10:17,000
If I bring people in through the back door without permission,

166
00:10:17,000 --> 00:10:18,600
it might cause some trouble.

167
00:10:19,160 --> 00:10:20,690
I'll get her settled first,

168
00:10:20,880 --> 00:10:22,610
then I'll come back for you two.

169
00:10:31,840 --> 00:10:35,000
I don't think I told you my name.

170
00:10:44,320 --> 00:10:45,650
Last night in the cabin,

171
00:10:45,720 --> 00:10:47,850
you told me when you were half-asleep.

172
00:10:48,360 --> 00:10:49,490
Have you forgotten?

173
00:10:50,320 --> 00:10:51,400
Is that so?

174
00:10:52,840 --> 00:10:54,680
Then you wouldn't have forgotten

175
00:10:54,680 --> 00:10:56,160
that my name is Shen Yi.

176
00:11:00,160 --> 00:11:02,760
I might not have been thinking clearly yesterday.

177
00:11:02,760 --> 00:11:04,000
I'm sorry.

178
00:11:04,200 --> 00:11:05,840
But I remember it now.

179
00:11:06,840 --> 00:11:07,520
Oh no.

180
00:11:07,560 --> 00:11:09,280
Is he really going to die?

181
00:11:13,000 --> 00:11:15,360
Excuse me.

182
00:11:15,600 --> 00:11:17,120
What's going on here?

183
00:11:22,560 --> 00:11:23,760
It has nothing to do with me.

184
00:11:23,760 --> 00:11:24,720
I'm telling you,

185
00:11:24,840 --> 00:11:26,640
my eldest brother is the backbone of the Hu family.

186
00:11:26,640 --> 00:11:27,120
Your medical hall treated him to death.

187
00:11:27,120 --> 00:11:27,880
He owns a restaurant.

188
00:11:27,880 --> 00:11:29,240
Tell us how you'll compensate us.

189
00:11:29,240 --> 00:11:30,440
Let go.

190
00:11:30,800 --> 00:11:31,840
Unbelievable.

191
00:11:33,040 --> 00:11:35,240
It's too early to say he's dead.

192
00:11:35,240 --> 00:11:37,440
He can still be saved. Let me take a look.

193
00:11:38,000 --> 00:11:39,360
Where did this woman come from?

194
00:11:39,360 --> 00:11:40,680
Don't touch my brother.

195
00:11:40,680 --> 00:11:43,600
Who knows what kind of suffering you'll put my brother through.

196
00:11:43,600 --> 00:11:46,320
You're stopping people from saving your brother.

197
00:11:46,320 --> 00:11:48,720
Could it be that you don't want him to live?

198
00:11:49,360 --> 00:11:51,480
What does our family business have to do with an outsider?

199
00:11:51,480 --> 00:11:52,320
Are you asking for a beating?

200
00:11:52,320 --> 00:11:52,800
Are you?

201
00:11:57,080 --> 00:11:57,600
You...

202
00:11:57,600 --> 00:12:00,260
In that case, why are you still blocking the way?

203
00:12:02,160 --> 00:12:04,560
Second Uncle, I think they have a point.

204
00:12:23,200 --> 00:12:24,600
It's only been one night.

205
00:12:24,760 --> 00:12:26,290
How could it worsen so fast?

206
00:12:26,920 --> 00:12:28,980
What medicine did you prescribe him?

207
00:12:29,840 --> 00:12:32,160
I have practiced medicine for years

208
00:12:32,720 --> 00:12:35,320
and treated thousands of patients.

209
00:12:35,560 --> 00:12:37,820
Since when can a little girl question me?

210
00:12:41,040 --> 00:12:42,160
Get out of my way.

211
00:12:42,920 --> 00:12:45,840
My patient is not for you to trifle with.

212
00:12:47,480 --> 00:12:49,000
My mentor is Lingyue of Gushan.

213
00:12:49,000 --> 00:12:51,200
You must have heard of her name.

214
00:13:11,560 --> 00:13:12,320
Xiang.

215
00:13:26,560 --> 00:13:27,920
Yi Yinan.

216
00:13:27,920 --> 00:13:28,400
Zheng, Chen, Luo, Deng.

217
00:13:27,920 --> 00:13:28,320
Xiao Xiaoxue, Que, Yi Yinan.

218
00:13:28,400 --> 00:13:30,530
Wu, Zhang, Li, Zheng, Chen, Luo, Deng.

219
00:13:28,400 --> 00:13:28,960
Xiao Xiaoxue, Yi Yinan.

220
00:13:56,640 --> 00:13:57,520
Ma, Miao, Lu, Ran.

221
00:13:57,520 --> 00:13:58,520
Ma, Miao, Lu, Ran.

222
00:14:02,400 --> 00:14:02,880
Pan, Xiu, Long.

223
00:14:02,880 --> 00:14:03,680
Pan, Xiu, Long.

224
00:14:02,880 --> 00:14:03,400
Lyu, Sun, Zhang, Meng,
